seller.description:
LET ME TRANSFORM YOUR INTERIOR / ARCHITECTURAL DESIGN INTO 3D REALITY !

Hello, I am Chami, working as an online freelancer in the Architectural 3d rendering field which includes realistic 3D renderings for interior exterior, walkthrough video for houses/ buildings/ backyard designs.

I am eager to convert your wishes into 3D visuals of the desired result. Using your architectural drawings as a starting point, I create realistic 3D rendering of your architectural design. 

Do you need to experience in professional architectural 3d rendering service ! Looking forward to collaborating with you.

reviews.comment: Janashi did an excellent job on providing, initially just the outside of the house, and then we added the interior rooms/floors as well.  She was patience with this old, non-techie lady.  Her work was turned around quickly and when I could not email them in the initial format she compressed them for me.  Resolution may have lost a bit but not much at all.  I would highly recommend her to anyone wanting architectural renderings.  You may find some cheaper, but I doubt with the attention to detail and willingness to gracefully make changes.

I've been there many, many times, have seen every detail of my "dream", but only in my imagination..... but with Janashi professional help, my vision became almost a reality.  Janashi did exceptionally good job converting 2D drawings of the buildings and a site plan into 3D Creation.  She has a great vision of the whole project and attention to details.  High grade CAD/3D Rendering skill.  Always on time with a project!   Great to communicate and easy about any changes to the project that may appear during the project.  She is absolutely very professional and your best choice when you need 3D Rendering done with the best results.  Thank you Janashi!

we were having a very hard time picturing what the exterior of our house would look like, and what colors to choose, and Janashi did an amazing job showing us what different colors would look like, and made it so much easier for us to make our decision!

Impressed with the quality of the design and walk thru video.   Design plans were created exactly as anticipated and the project looks great.  Easy to work with and made minor revisions quickly to make the project perfect.   I highly recommend using Janashl for any 3D Design or interior Design work you may need.
I didn't know anyone in my area that did this kind of thing, so glad I found Fiverr will certainly use in the future.
